The '''Aldereenian Consulate''' was the [[Aldereenian]] embassy to the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. It was located on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], 200 [[Kilometer/Legends|kilometers]] from [[Cantham House/Legends|Cantham House]].

